      • summarize

        public static java.lang.Long summarize(FBSummarizationTaskDetails details)
        Create and schedule facebook summarization task with the given details. If details have taskId given, the task will not be re-added, and will simply be (re-)scheduled. If the details contains no back-ends, default back-ends will be added. See DEFAULT_CAPABILITIES
        Parameters:
        details - details of the task, if profile object is given, it will be ignored.
        Returns:
        the id of the generated task or null on failure
